tains recognition. Commercial enterprises as well as non-profit organisations and public social welfare centres can apply for recognition. Your company can either carry out activities exclusively with service vouchers or in addition to other activities.</p><p>In order to become a recognised company, you must meet a number of conditions. For example, you must take part in an information session, pay a deposit of EUR 25,000 and add an accurate business plan in accordance with the regulations on service vouchers. General conditions also apply.</p><p>After obtaining recognition, you have to recruit employees who want to work as service voucher employees. They may also be foreign workers, provided they have a valid work permit. These employees must also meet certain conditions. Certain categories of employees may not be recruited through a service voucher employment contract. In addition, they may only perform a specific number of defined tasks.</p>"},"naam":{"nl":"Voorwaarden","nl-BE-x-formal":"Voorwaarden","en":"Requirements","nl-BE-x-generated-informal":"Voorwaarden"},"@type":"Voorwaarde","order":0}],"procedures":[{"naam":{"nl-BE-x-formal":"Procedure","nl-BE-x-generated-informal":"Procedure","en":"Procedure","nl":"Procedure"},"beschrijving":{"nl":"<p>U vraagt uw erkenning aan in het gewest waar u de dienstencheque-activiteiten wilt uitvoeren. Wilt u als bedrijf een <a href=\"https://www.dev-vlaanderen.be/consumentenzaken/een-dienstencheque-onderneming-opstarten-en-beheren/voorwaarden-om-een-dienstencheque-onderneming-op-te-richten\"><strong>erkenning aanvragen</strong> voor het Vlaamse Gewest</a>, dan moet u volgende stappen ondernemen</p><ul><li>Woon de informatiesessie bij</li><li>Betaal de borgsom</li><li>Stel het ondernemingsplan op</li><li>Dien het erkenningsformulier in</li></ul>","nl-BE-x-generated-informal":"<p>Je vraagt jouw erkenning aan in het gewest waar je de dienstencheque-activiteiten wilt uitvoeren. Wil je als bedrijf een <a href=\"https://www.dev-vlaa